reviewText:
The concept is great and you can build the very sophisticated road and transport network (when you learn how to do it) but  when you do it then goes a big dissappointment:
1) it crashes very often due to some development errors;
2) the schedules are no use because the vehicles go very slowly;
3) the passangers can't wait for one line only even if there are two in the same direction from the same stop;
4) the night graphic makes it difficult to bulid anything and having a big city you must wait about an hour for a day, even on the quick mode (and I have a new fact computer).

